Merge pull request #6 from VictorRodriguez/master

Rename cpuid tool to msr-cpuid to avoid a conflict

Change name of cpuid tools to msr-cpuid

This change is necesary sinc ethe name has conflicts with other open
sourse projects already installed in the operating system:

http://pkgs.fedoraproject.org/cgit/rpms/cpuid.git/tree/cpuid.spec

Even RH cahnge the name of the binary to avoid conlficts:

http://pkgs.fedoraproject.org/cgit/rpms/msr-tools.git/tree/msr-tools.spec

install -D cpuid %{buildroot}%{_sbindir}/msr-cpuid

Signed-off-by: Victor Rodriguez <victor.rodriguez.bahena@intel.com>

Merge pull request #5 from bryteise/master

Use autotools for building

Use autotools for building

This change replaces the Makefile with autoconf and automake
configuration files.

The motivation for this change was to support standard conventions for
passing CFLAGS and DESTDIR options while also increasing portability and
adding build time dependency checks.
